<center><strong>The Armory</strong></center>
Because of the severe weight restriction imposed on the class, part of playing a monk succesfully involves knowing your equipment. 
While there is certainly not as much of a variety of gear available for the class, however, there are several alternatives that, 
depending upon your needs, do need to be considered (such as resists, AC, etc.).  As such I have compiled here a list of <strong>
all</strong> monkable gear.  Some, for obvious reasons, you may never wear (too heavy, bonuses to irrelevant stats, etc.), but 
I feel it's better to give you all of the choices and let you decide rather than make that decision for you.
<p>
The equipment database is a work-in-progress.  If you have a piece of equipment that is not listed, please feel free to send it 
in to <a href=mailto:sensei@thedojo.extropian.org>me</a>.
<p>
